file.name: parameters_overloading.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  title: Projects API
  version: 1.0.0
paths:
  /projects/{id}:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: id
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int64
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 'Success'
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SampleResponse'
  /projects/{uid}:
    get:
      parameters:
        - in: path
          name: uid
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            format: uuid
      responses:
        '200':
          description: 'Success'
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/SampleResponse'
components:
  schemas:
    SampleResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
        uid:
          type: string
        name:
          type: string
      required:
        - id
        - uid
        - name
